      propertyPath: tutorialMessages.Array.size
      value: 5
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4015757124078104856, guid: 0c0850554bd874043bf44d91462d4653,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: tutorialMessages.Array.data[0]
      value: 'The goal of this game is to defeat a giant enemy.

        You lose
        if your HP drops to 0.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4015757124078104856, guid: 0c0850554bd874043bf44d91462d4653,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: tutorialMessages.Array.data[1]
      value: 'You can heal yourself by pressing the trigger button while holding
        a potion.

        You can only attack while holding a weapon and holding
        down the trigger button.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4015757124078104856, guid: 0c0850554bd874043bf44d91462d4653,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: tutorialMessages.Array.data[2]
      value: You can open the pause menu by pressing the A/X button.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4015757124078104856, guid: 0c0850554bd874043bf44d91462d4653,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: tutorialMessages.Array.data[3]
      value: 'There are slots around your waist for equipping items.

        Equip
        potions in the potion slot and weapons in the weapon slot.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4015757124078104856, guid: 0c0850554bd874043bf44d91462d4653,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: tutorialMessages.Array.data[4]
      value: 'Your quest is about to begin!

        Do not forget your weapons and
        potions.

        Press Start when you are ready! '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
